name: ZK Projects Meet & Greet
description: After the ZK Week Kickoff, ZK teams will congregate in the Chedi Ballroom (aka the coworking space) for a ZK Projects Meet and Greet from 8:15 - 9:30PM. This might be especially interesting for those who are potentially interested in the ZK Hackathon the following weekend, which has several tracks (building on zkRollups, ZK Passport, and the Nova proving system).
